    </span>
      <a class="description_present" title="- Do you have tests?
- What kind of tests do you write/create?
- What software do you use for the tests?
- When do you write/create them? While you&#39;re still prototyping or after you&#39;ve got a user interface that you like?

I&#39;ve been using a simple functional reactive design with mithril.js + [meiosis](https://meiosis.js.org/), so I&#39;m particularly interested in solutions that work well with that kind of design." href="/s/f1vgfq/how_do_you_test_your_client_side_web">&#x2636;</a>
